window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Don't miss the grand finale of this best-selling super-harem phenomenon!</p> <p>After what happened in Vermont, there was only one thing left to do. A great purge was in order, a fresh start for the Cherry Blossom Girls. No matter where it took us, it needed to happen.</p> <p>For Fiona, for my parents, and for those who would lose their lives over the course of the following weeks.</p> <p>Out with the old and in with the new. Our enemies had to go.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
